<ul>
<li><i>Was previously Knight of the Légion d'honneur (since 2004)</i></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Ordre_national_du_M%C3%A9rite" title="Ordre national du Mérite">Grand Cross of the <i>Ordre national du Mérite</i></a> (2007 - Automatic when taking office)</li>
</ul>
<p><a name="Other_countries" id="Other_countries"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Nicolas_Sarkozy&amp;action=edit&amp;section=35" title="Edit section: Other countries">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Other countries</span></h3>
