<li><span class="languageicon" style="font-size:0.95em; font-weight:bold; color:#555;">(English)</span> <a href="http://vacarme.eu.org/article1507.html" class="external text" title="http://vacarme.eu.org/article1507.html" rel="nofollow">On the so-called "rupture" by Sarkozy</a>, Mathieu Potte-Bonneville &amp; Pierre Zaoui, <i><a href="/w/index.php?title=Vacarme&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Vacarme (page does not exist)">Vacarme</a></i> n°41, Winter 2007</li>
