President_of_Ireland" title="President of Ireland">IE</a>) · <a href="/wiki/Giorgio_Napolitano" title="Giorgio Napolitano">Napolitano</a> (<a href="/wiki/President_of_the_Italian_Republic" title="President of the Italian Republic">IT</a>) · <a href="/wiki/Valdis_Zatlers" title="Valdis Zatlers">Zatlers</a> (<a href="/wiki/List_of_Presidents_of_Latvia" title="List of Presidents of Latvia">LV</a>) · <a href="/wiki/Valdas_Adamkus" title="Valdas Adamkus">Adamkus</a> (<a href="/wiki/List_of_rulers_of_Lithuania" title="List of rulers of Lithuania">LT</a>) · <a href="/wiki/Henri,_Grand_Duke_of_Luxembourg" title="Henri, Grand Duke of Luxembourg">Henri</a> (<a href="/wiki/Grand_Duke_of_Luxembourg" title="Grand Duke of Luxembourg">LU</a><sup>2</sup>) · <a href="/wiki/George_Abela" title="George Abela">Abela</a> (<a href="/wiki/President_of_Malta" title="President of Malta">MT</a>) · <a href="/wiki/Beatrix_of_the_Netherlands" title="Beatrix of the Netherlands">Beatrix</a> (<a href="/wiki/Monarchy_of_the_Netherlands" title="Monarchy of the Netherlands">NL</a><sup>2</sup>) · <a href="/wiki/Lech_Kaczy%C5%84ski" title="Lech Kaczyński">Kaczyński</a> (<a href="/wiki/President_of_the_Republic_of_Poland" title="President of the Republic of Poland">PL</a>) · <a href="/wiki/An%C3%ADbal_Cavaco_Silva" title="Aníbal Cavaco Silva">Cavaco Silva</a> (<a href="/wiki/President_of_Portugal" title="President of Portugal">PT</a>) · <a href="/wiki/Traian_B%C4%83sescu" title="Traian Băsescu">Băsescu</a> (<a href="/wiki/President_of_Romania" title="President of Romania">RO</a>) · <a href="/wiki/Ivan_Ga%C5%A1parovi%C4%8D" title="Ivan Gašparovič">Gašparovič</a> (<a href="/wiki/List_of_Presidents_of_Slovakia" title="List of Presidents of Slovakia">SK</a>) · <a href="/wiki/Danilo_T%C3%BCrk" title="Danilo Türk">Türk</a> (<a href="/wiki/President_of_Slovenia" title="President of Slovenia">SI</a>) · <a href="/wiki/Juan_Carlos_I_of_Spain" title="Juan Carlos I of Spain">Juan Carlos I</a> (<a href="/wiki/Monarchy_of_Spain" title="Monarchy of Spain">ES</a><sup>2</sup>) · <a href="/wiki/Carl_XVI_Gustaf_of_Sweden" title="Carl XVI Gustaf of Sweden">Carl XVI Gustaf</a> (<a href="/wiki/Monarchy_of_Sweden" title="Monarchy of Sweden">SE</a><sup>2</sup>) · <a href="/wiki/Elizabeth_II_of_the_United_Kingdom" title="Elizabeth II of the United Kingdom">Elizabeth II</a> (<a href="/wiki/Monarchy_of_the_United_Kingdom" title="Monarchy of the United Kingdom">UK</a><sup>2</sup>)</div>
